title: The Pepper Sisters
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Beer/Wine, Mexican, Southwestern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. All beans are vegan, as are the sides of posole and house salad that come with every entree. Vegan sopapilla served meal. Potato flautas and eggplant tostads, and a other few entrees that are marked as able to be veganized. Bright, warm atmosphere. Free chips and salsa if you state beforehand that you will be paying in cash.
